reviewText: Wish I read the description... can't play them and cannot return. Why would these be available in a country that can't play them, anyway?
The discs will NOT play!!! Very, VERY unhappy.
I didn't realize these DVDs could not be used in American DVD players and seller will not give refund if package has been opened. So I'm stuck with a box set that I can't use:-(
I am not able to watch them because I didn't realize they where from the UK so they don't work on US DVD players. So it was a waste of money!
